 only be changed indirectly, which makes simple progress\nupdates inconvenient during normal use.\n\nUsers need a direct way to mark a task as done or not done while keeping\nthe same task numbering shown in list output.\n\nAdd parser support for mark and unmark commands, execute task state\nupdates through dedicated command classes, and save changes immediately.\n\nKeep user feedback explicit after each status update and add tests for\nboth parsing and command execution so valid and invalid inputs are covered.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":109,"deletions":1},"test-code":{"insertions":128,"deletions":1}}},{"hash":"acf28081e523ac8d5bb25e8508747a0383d2d46d","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #18 from heeelol/JiaWei-Add-Mark-and-mark-logic","messageBody":"Add mark and unmark task commands","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}}]},{"date":"2026-03-18T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"558b0b58a4b2396a2e894046e59f6b02f973afc5","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge branch \u0027AY2526S2-CS2113-W11-2:master\u0027 into master","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}}]},{"date":"2026-03-25T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"68328bf6984bf9af36bb7b7e698081971a0ed833","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #34 from Huang-Hau-Shuan/add-weightage","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}}]},{"date":"2026-03-26T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"9d8d448f455900d88be7517ea7f06104f2647164","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge branch \u0027AY2526S2-CS2113-W11-2:master\u0027 into master","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"5f1cdb4ec58e25a81b25272e32f013a14f602727","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Add list /deadlines command and UI","messageBody":"Introduce a ListDeadlinesCommand and wire parsing support for a new \"list /deadlines\" filter.\n\nParser now delegates list handling to parseList, returning ListDeadlinesCommand for the /deadlines filter or throwing a ModuleSyncException for unknown filters.\n\nUi gains showDeadlineList which gathers Deadline tasks across modules, sorts them by due date, and prints an ordered upcoming-deadlines view (includes a small DeadlineEntry helper class).\n\nThis change enables a focused deadline view to help users plan their week.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":96,"deletions":9}}},{"hash":"bec4733fb76cd7d2bb137d269f0f8bb8a9cc5ee3","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Add assertions and docs for list /deadlines","messageBody":"Document the new `list /deadlines` feature in DeveloperGuide and harden related code.\n\nAdded a detailed feature section describing parsing, command flow, and UI behavior. Introduced null-check assertions and sanity checks: in ListDeadlinesCommand.execute, Parser.parseList (input non-empty and command creation), and Ui.showDeadlineList (module/task/deadline non-null and sorted-order verification).\n\nAlso refactored command instantiation in Parser for clearer assertions. These changes improve robustness and provide design documentation for the deadlines listing feature.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":23,"deletions":3},"docs":{"insertions":71,"deletions":0}}},{"hash":"b6dc6188a40f1ae9f45eda3a90864b8f48062849","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #35 from heeelol/JiaWei-Deadline-List","messageBody":"Implement list /deadlines command and enhance UI for deadlines","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"97f18e7e6ceac4f6e015065f644661aaf933ce6a","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge branch \u0027AY2526S2-CS2113-W11-2:master\u0027 into master","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"bf17e12b91529072bd565dc0eb06b1c4b77a79ef","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge branch \u0027master\u0027 of https://github.com/heeelol/tp","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}}]},{"date":"2026-03-31T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"713e16db2d819ecbcc8